<L>__{exterior quadrangle night}
<B>__{close shot prew}
<A>__{continuing the taps. there are tears in his eyes now.}
<L>__{exterior barracks steps night}
<B>__{medium shot}
<A>__{a half dozen men are sitting on the steps, listening, among them stark and wilson. stark shakes his head sadly.}
<L>__{exterior company street night}
<B>__{medium close shot warden}
<A>__{listening now on the porch alongside the street.}
<L>__{exterior barracks area night}
<B>__{long shot}
<A>__{several groups of two and three scattered about. they are standing in no particular places, as if they have been walking and stopped suddenly. they are all looking toward the bugler.}
